server.name: AX41-NVMe
server.description: The AX41-NVMe Dedicated Root Server houses the powerful third generation Ryzen™ 5 3600 CPU from AMD, which is based on Zen 2 architecture. With two speedy 512 NVME SSDs and 64 GB of DDR4 RAM, this model is perfect for creative workloads and applications that have high multi-threading requirements.
server.cpu_fullname: AMD Ryzen™ 5 3600 Hexa-Core Matisse (Zen2) Simultaneous Multithreading
server.hdd_hr: 2x 512 GB NVMe SSD

server.name: EX44
server.description: The EX44 Dedicated server’s hidden gem is the Intel® Core™ i5-13500 processor. This 13th generation chip with hyper-threading boasts 6 powerful performance cores and 8 energy-efficient cores, and together they provide stunning overall performance. Shining alongside the i5-13500 is 64 GB of DDR4 RAM and two blazingly quick 512 GB Gen4 NVMe SSDs. This dazzling package pushes the definition of an entry level server; it will more than suit your needs for a variety of use cases, and all at a brilliant price.
server.cpu_fullname: Intel® Core™ i5-13500 14-Core Raptor Lake-S incl. Hyper-Threading Technology
server.hdd_hr: 2x 512 GB NVMe SSD (Gen4)

server.name: AX42
server.description: The Dedicated Server AX42 is not only powerful, but also remarkably efficient and significantly reduces the ecological footprint thanks to its low energy consumption. It houses the impressive AMD Ryzen™ 7 PRO 8700GE octa-core “Phoenix 1” (Zen4) processor. In combination with the AMD Ryzen™ AI engine, the CPU opens a world of possibilities for artificial intelligence and ensures that users will experience smooth multitasking, higher productivity and innovative support for complex tasks. With a generous 2 x 32 GB of DDR5 ECC UDIMM RAM, the Dedicated Server AX42 handles applications at high speed. Two 512 GB Gen4 NVMe SSDs in a software RAID 1 configuration also provide secure storage and plenty of it.
server.cpu_fullname: AMD Ryzen™ 7 PRO 8700GE  Octa-Core Phoenix 1 (Zen4) Simultaneous Multithreading
server.hdd_hr: 2x 512 GB NVMe SSD (Gen4)

server.name: AX52
server.description: The AX52 Dedicated Server provides remarkable performance with its AMD Ryzen™ 7 7700 processor, which is based on Zen4 architecture. It’s well-suited for a wide range of multi-threading intense workloads thanks to its 8 cores and 16 threads. The AX52 houses 64 GB of DDR5 RAM, making it one of the first Hetzner server models based on the new DDR5 generation of memory. Last but certainly not least, it includes two fast 1 TB Gen4 NVMe SSDs, making the AX52 a perfect all around performer.
server.cpu_fullname: AMD Ryzen™ 7 7700 Octa-Core Raphael (Zen 4) Simultaneous Multithreading
server.hdd_hr: 2x 1 TB NVMe SSD (Gen4)

server.name: EX101
server.description: The EX101 Dedicated Server houses the high-end Intel® i9-13900 processor and displays impressive performance on a wide range of applications thanks to its hybrid architecture. It has both energy efficient cores, which process background workloads, and powerful performance cores, which are designed for intense workloads, such as data analysis and AI. Larger L2 and L3 caches significantly speed up data retrieval. We’ve cleverly equipped the EX101 with not just any RAM, but 64 GB of DDR5 ECC RAM, giving the extra reliability of error correction code plus the boosted performance of DDR5. It’s one of the first Hetzner server models with this type of memory. This power pack of a server also comes with two fast 1.92 TB Datacenter Gen4 NVMe SSDs to give you lots of storage.
server.cpu_fullname: Intel® Core™ i9-13900 24-Core Raptor Lake-S incl. Hyper-Threading Technology
server.hdd_hr: 2x 1.92 TB NVMe SSD Datacenter Edition (Gen 4)

server.name: AX102
server.description: The AX102 Dedicated Server features the AMD Ryzen™ 9 7950X3D with asymmetric design. One set of 8 cores are mounted with AMD's innovative 3D V-Cache technology for minimized latency and workloads that require more memory; the other group of 8 cores is designed for tasks that require higher clock speeds. We’ve mounted the AX102 with 128 GB of DDR5 ECC RAM. In addition to the classic ECC (error correction code), which protects data both on the memory module and during transfer, the new DDR5 memory generation uses the on-die ECC method. This method carries out independent error correction directly on the DRAM chip, giving you greatly optimized reliability and data integrity.
server.cpu_fullname: AMD Ryzen™ 9 7950X3D 16 Core Raphael (Zen 4) with AMD 3D V-Cache™ Technology
server.hdd_hr: 2x 1.92 TB NVMe SSD Datacenter Edition (Gen4)

server.name: SX65
server.description: The Dedicated Storage Server SX65 provides you with infrastructure for professional server management. It comes with 2 x 1 TB (Gen3) NVMe SSDs for lightning-fast access plus 4 x 22 TB SATA HDDs to provide roomy data capacity. All HDDs in this model are hotswap capable, meaning that you can swap out the drives without downtime. For memory, the base configuration is equipped with 64 GB of DDR4 ECC RAM, which you can increase to as much as 128 GB.
server.cpu_fullname: AMD Ryzen™ 7 3700X Octa-Core Matisse (Zen2) Simultaneous Multithreading
server.hdd_hr: 4x 22 TB SATA HDD, 2x 1 TB (Gen3) SSD

server.name: EX130-R
server.description: The Dedicated Server EX130-R is equipped with the Intel® Xeon® Gold 5412U 24-core processor for intense and growing workloads. Thanks to its base configuration, which has 2 x 1.92 TB Datacenter Edition NVMe SSDs and 256 GB of DDR5 ECC reg. RAM, it is ideal for tasks that require high processing power and lightning-fast data memory speeds. You can scale up the DDR5 ECC reg. RAM in blocks, up to 768 GB of it. And configurations can bulk up on storage, too - add up to 6 additional Datacenter Edition NVMe SSDs or 2 additional SATA Enterprise HDDs of various sizes.
server.cpu_fullname: Intel® Xeon™ Gold 5412U Sapphire Rapids incl. Hyper-Threading Technology
server.hdd_hr: 2x 1.92 TB NVMe SSD Datacenter Edition (Gen 4)

server.name: EX130-S
server.description: The Dedicated Server EX130-S is equipped with the Intel® Xeon® Gold 5412U 24-core processor for intense and growing workloads and, with its 2 x 3.84 TB Datacenter Edition NVMe SSDs and 128 GB DDR5 ECC reg. RAM, it is especially suitable for rapidly growing storage-intense tasks, such as big data analytics. And configurations can bulk up on storage, too - add up to 6 additional Datacenter Edition NVMe SSDs or 2 additional SATA Enterprise HDDs of various sizes. The RAM can also be scaled up in blocks to 768 GB of DDR5 ECC reg.
server.cpu_fullname: Intel® Xeon™ Gold 5412U Sapphire Rapids incl. Hyper-Threading Technology
server.hdd_hr: 2x 3.84 TB NVMe SSD Datacenter Edition (Gen 4)

server.name: RX170
server.description: 80 cores make quick work of even the most CPU-intensive tasks. The Ampere ® Altra ® CPU, which uses Arm64 architecture, pushes the envelop of parallelization, and provides reliable performance and has the added benefit of wasting less energy, which can also aid performance. The RX170 is the ideal addition to any serious system with high workload demands. With 128 GB DDR4 registered ECC memory modules and 2x 960GB NVMe SSD, the smaller model RX170 also meets the high expectations that are nowadays put on datacenter-grade products.
server.hdd_hr: 2x 960 GB Datacenter NVMe SSD

server.name: GEX44
server.description: With the new Dedicated Server GEX44, you’ll experience the epic performance and computing power of a GPU; its processing architecture enables it to process many tasks in parallel, making it ideal for processing large and complex amounts of data especially quickly and efficiently. The new GPU Server GEX44 houses a heavy-duty NVIDIA RTX™ 4000 SFF Ada generation graphics card with 20 GB of GDDR6 ECC GPU memory, offering a wide range of artificial intelligence options at the best price. The GEX44 wouldn’t be complete without its Intel® Core™ i5-13500 processor from the 13th “Raptor Lake” generation with Hyper-Threading Technology Virtualization (Intel-VT), which houses an impressive 6 performance cores and 8 efficiency cores. Two speedy 1.92 TB Gen3 Datacenter Edition NVMe SSDs plus 64 GB of DDR4 RAM complete this powerhouse of a GPU server.
server.cpu_fullname: Intel® Core™ i5-13500 14-Core Raptor Lake-S incl. Hyper-Threading Technology
server.hdd_hr: 2x 1.92 TB NVMe SSD (Gen3)

server.name: DX153
server.description:
The Dedicated Server Dell PowerEdge™ R660 DX153 delivers dependability with its dual Intel® Xeon® Silver 4410Y 12-core “Sapphire Rapids” CPUs; you’ll get solid performance that comes with the brand name’s reputation. For memory, you can rely on tried and true 64 GB of DDR5 ECC reg. RAM on the DX153; and if your use case requires more, you can add up to 2048 GB of it.

The DX153 comes with all the flexibilities and features you would expect from high-grade hardware, allowing you to scale intelligently and simplify your administration.

You can scale your storage as needed, too; get NVMe-SSDs or SATA SSDs in an array of sizes. The DX153 supports hot swapping, so you can exchange or add drives while your system is running:
server.cpu_fullname: 2x Intel® Xeon® Silver 4410Y 12-Core, Sapphire Rapids inkl. Hyper-Threading-Technologie
server.hdd_hr: 10x optional (at additional cost)

server.name: AX162-R
server.description: The Dedicated Server AX162-R is mounted with the AMD EPYC™ Genoa 9454P 48-core, 4th generation processor, which is designed for intense workloads that require parallel processing. Its standard configuration comes with 256 GB of DDR5 ECC reg. RAM to speed up your task executions and file access speeds, plus 2 x 1.92 TB Gen4 Datacenter Edition NVMe SSDs. You can also scale up the memory in increments to an unbelieveable total of 1152 GB of DDR5 ECC reg. RAM. And if you need more storage capacity, you can add up to 8 Datacenter Edition NVMe SSDs or 2 SATA Enterprise HDDs in various sizes.
server.cpu_fullname: AMD EPYC™ 9454P 48-Core Genoa (Zen4) incl. Simultaneous Multithreading
server.hdd_hr: 2x 1.92 TB NVMe SSD Datacenter Edition (Gen 4)

server.name: AX162-S
server.description: The Dedicated Server AX162-S is mounted with the AMD EPYC™ Genoa 9454P 48-core, 4th generation processor, which is designed for intense workloads that require parallel processing. Its storage heavy configurate is ideal for use cases with quickly growing storage requirements: it comes with 2 x 3.84 Datacenter Edition NVMe SSDs and 128 GB of DDR5 ECC reg. RAM. And if you need even more storage capacity, you can add up to 8 Datacenter Edition NVMe SSDs or 2 SATA Enterprise HDDs in various sizes. Plus, you can scale up the memory in increments to an unbelieveable total of 1152 GB of DDR5 ECC reg. RAM.
server.cpu_fullname: AMD EPYC™ 9454P 48-Core Genoa (Zen4) incl. Simultaneous Multithreading
server.hdd_hr: 2x 3.84 TB NVMe SSD Datacenter Edition (Gen 4)

server.name: SX135
server.description: The Dedicated Storage Server SX135 gives you ample room to grow with its 8 x 22 TB SATA HDDs; they’re all hotswap capable, meaning you can swap out the drives without downtime. For rapid read and write speeds, you can rely on its 2 x 1.92 TB (Gen3) NVMe Datacenter Editon SSDs. Combine all that with 128 GB of DDR4 ECC RAM, and you’ve got the perfect partner for massive storage management.
server.hdd_hr: 8x 22 TB  SATA HDD, 2x 1.92 TB SSD Datacenter Edition (Gen3)

server.name: RX220
server.description: 80 cores make quick work of even the most CPU-intensive tasks. The Ampere ® Altra ® CPU, which uses Arm64 architecture, pushes the envelop of parallelization, and provides reliable performance and has the added benefit of wasting less energy, which can also aid performance. The RX220 is the ideal addition to any serious system with high workload demands. With 256 GB DDR4 registered ECC memory modules and 2x 3.84 TB NVMe SSD, the RX220 meets the high expectations that are nowadays put on datacenter-grade products.
server.hdd_hr: 2x 3,84 TB Datacenter NVMe SSD

server.name: DX182
server.description:
The Dell PowerEdge™ R6615 DX182 relies on an AMD EPYC™ 9454P CPU. With its impressive 48 cores of Genoa (Zen4) architecture, this processor provides the power you need for demanding tasks. Thanks to simultaneous multithreading and virtualization technology (AMD-V), you can handle multiple tasks simultaneously and make the most of your resources.

This dedicated server is perfect for processing workloads such as virtualization, HCI architecture, and Network Functions Virtualization, making it suitable for Big Data, Artificial Intelligence, and rendering, among others.

Benefit from the versatility and flexibility of this efficient model. For example, the RAM can be expanded to 1152 GB DDR5 ECC reg. and the number of storage can be individually adapted to your requirements. A total of up to ten drives can be integrated for an additional charge:
server.cpu_fullname: AMD EPYC™ 9454P 48-Core Genoa (Zen4) incl. Simultaneous Multithreading
server.hdd_hr: 10x optional (at additional cost)

server.name: DX293
server.description:
The Dell PowerEdge™ R660 DX293 is the high-end solution on brand hardware level.

This dedicated server relies on two Intel® Xeon® Gold 6438Y+ processors with 32 cores each based on the Sapphire Rapids-SP architecture and is especially suited for memory-intensive and mission-critical tasks as well as real-time analytics. Hyper-Threading technology also lets you process your workloads faster and more efficiently. With Intel-VT, you can also manage your resources efficiently and flexibly.

Benefit from the versatility and flexibility of this efficient model. The RAM can be increased to 2048 GB DDR5 ECC reg. to maximize performance. You can also configure the drives individually according to your wishes. You can integrate a total of up to ten drives for an additional charge:
server.cpu_fullname: 2x Intel® Xeon® Gold 6438Y+ 32-Core Sapphire Rapids incl. Hyper-Threading-Technology
server.hdd_hr: 10x optional (at additional cost)

server.name: SX295
server.description: The Dedicated Storage Server SX295 fulfils all professional storage requirements with 2 x 7.68 TB (Gen4) NVMe Datacenter Edition SSDs and 14 x 22 TB SATA HDDs. The base model comes with 256 GB of DDR4 ECC reg. RAM, but you can expand this to as much as 1024 GB. The SX295 and its impressive AMD EPYC™ 7502P 32-core “Rome” (Zen2) CPU can reliably handle large amounts of data around the clock, making it ideal for data archiving, database hosting, multimedia storage, and streaming or as an object storage solution.
server.hdd_hr: 14x 22 TB SATA HDD, 2x 7.68 TB Datacenter Edition SSD (Gen4)

server.name: GEX130
server.description: Discover the next level of performance with the new GEX130 dedicated GPU server. Equipped with the NVIDIA RTX™ 6000 Ada generation graphics card, it can put ideas into practice even faster and highly complex tasks can be completed efficiently. In addition to 48 GB of GPU Memory, 568 Tensor Cores, 142 RT Cores and 18176 CUDA Cores ensure this. The GEX130 is the ideal choice for computationally intensive tasks such as training AI models, processing large data sets and applications in image and speech processing. It meets the highest requirements for speed and efficiency – perfect for those who strive for top performance to realize innovative solutions.
server.cpu_fullname: Intel® Xeon™ Gold 5412U Sapphire Rapids incl. Hyper-Threading Technology
server.hdd_hr: 2x 1.92 TB NVMe SSD Datacenter Edition
